{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The thing that struck me was with this guide who was-- he had been there since he was a Signal Corps photographer-- and he had been all over the camp so he knew where things were.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of the feelings that I had was that it was like a riot to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- where-- see, we had not got into the main part of the camp yet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had been on the periphery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we got inside the camp on the other side of the moat, where I said there were some SS guys laying on the moat that evidently had been killed by the inmates-- they just were laying there dead.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there was the fence, barbed-wire fence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these inmates were-- they weren't fighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were so happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the Americans were being kissed and hugged and thrown up in the air and all this kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the noise was-- was scary, like a football game, a roar, a roar, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I felt-- I only had a pistol.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all I was armed with, was a 45.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I felt like I needed more firepower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I ju-- for some reason this scared me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just-- it just scared me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were, you know, a couple of thousand people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could see- I could see helmeted Americans in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew they weren't in harm's way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they all had rifles with bayonets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of them had machine guns.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Americans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were-- they were in-- these were the liberators inside with the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what they were trying to do was calm everybody down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there were officers inside and-- and probably 150 American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
